snippet.title: USA: Anti-Armenian message displayed from plane during LA genocide commemoration

localized.description:
A plane dragging the message "stop Armenian lies" flew over thousands of commemorators, who had gathered to mark the 101st anniversary of the Armenian Genocide, outside the Turkish consulate at Wilshire Boulevard in Los Angeles, on Sunday.
